{"tid":545972,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[差啲中伏]有開Find My IPhone的人請小心","createTime":"2018-01-31T05:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T03:58:14.000Z","uid":12231,"like":310,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"15e5e65254134e6d7ccb98d653e3a16cdf21f4e2","tid":545972,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n話說幾個月前俾人偷咗部iphone6 就即刻開find my iPhone 入 lost mode<br />\n<br />\n一直都知iPhone就算洗咗機都會要求使用者log in返上一手機主的apple ID先可以用到部機<br />\n<br />\n事隔咁耐都預咗拎唔返部手機 直至琴日收到find my iPhone話部手機話online 就入find my iphone睇下佢去咗地球邊到 發現佢去咗GMT-6的地區（但冇顯示到準確的國家/位置） <br />\n<br />\n今日就收到以下message:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/125051_e9991dc05702cabb436d2f0c3154512d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F125051_e9991dc05702cabb436d2f0c3154512d.png&h=ec7ca0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後就拿拿聲log in等條仆街用唔到部手機 好在唔太記得個密碼 錯多2次就發現有啲唔對路<br />\n<br />\n個message條link後面做咩有kjtsd? 就再開條link 發現條link原來駁咗去vpn <br />\n<br />\n即刻大叫「屌你老母 差啲就中伏」嬲嬲地就去佢個login page個ID打：FuckYou!StolenMyiPhone PW打: YouSunoftheBeach<br />\n<br />\n啱先諗著cap圖時 已經發現：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/125904_c5e187ad5a29c3f53063cdc08b5dd142.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F125904_c5e187ad5a29c3f53063cdc08b5dd142.png&h=ab0798dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特此警惕各位巴絲打 差啲就俾人拎到個Apple ID<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0852db690896100afd54902c1667a529c5156424","tid":545972,"uid":81308,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"見到條link又hk又cn咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4317b1ea4d940b84843a26811507d9bf531eb031","tid":545972,"uid":143260,"like":264,"dislike":2,"score":262,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-